basic_info.description:
# Overview
Build and deploy complete frontend websites in one click, powered by a cloud-based AI coder.

# Description
Meet **Infinite Monkey Coder**, your always-on AI agent for frontend development.  
Tired of starting from scratch, wiring tools together, or handling deployments yourself?  
Infinite Monkey Coder takes your idea, **writes the frontend code**, and **automatically deploys it to Mule Pages**—all in one smooth flow.  

**No setup. No context switching. Just results.**  
Focus on what you want to build, and let the agent handle the rest from code to cloud.  

Turn ideas into live websites faster than ever—let’s ship something great
basic_info.short_description: Turns ideas into live, deployed frontend websites.
